description: A heavy mithril hatch secures the jail cells from the rest of the outpost.  The only source of light is a small griffin-shaped lantern sitting on top of a desk.  On the rear wall a large notice board is covered with warrants and wanted posters.  The port side is lined with two sturdy iron holding cells.  A collection set of chains and shackles are on display at the rear of the room, while almost hidden away in the far corner, three skeletons still dangle from their restraints.
title: [The Alliance Jail Cell]
